OL,3,CCoventry City promoted to the Premier
OL,4,CLeague for first time since 2001
OL,6,FCoventry City have been promoted to
OL,7,Fthe Premier League for the first time
OL,8,Fin 25 years.
OL,10,FIt comes after the Sky Blues drew 1-1
OL,11,Fagainst Blackburn.
OL,13,FAfter a goal-less first half Blackburn
OL,14,Ftook the lead, but an 83rd minute goal
OL,15,Ffrom Bobby Thomas secured the draw
OL,16,Fthey need to guarantee promotion.
OL,18,FFor those travelling Coventry fans who
OL,19,Fmade the 260 mile round trip, tonight
OL,20,Fmarks an occasion that they'll never
OL,21,Fforget.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
