OL,3,CCoventry City promoted to the Premier
OL,4,CLeague for first time since 2001
OL,6,FIt's their first time back since 2001,
OL,7,Fwhen they were relegated along with
OL,8,FBradford City and Manchester City
OL,9,Funder Gordon Strachan.
OL,11,FSince then the club have been
OL,12,Frelegated all the way down to League
OL,13,FTwo and faced financial crises and
OL,14,Fadministration battles. It was only
OL,15,Flast year when the club became the
OL,16,Fowner of its home stadium after so
OL,17,Fmuch uncertainty around their home.
OL,19,FNow the supporters can revel in the
OL,20,Fgood times with a return to the top
OL,21,Fflight.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
